<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870604-0018 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:Allied Products Corp.</HL><DD> 06/04/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> WNEWS ADP </IN><DATELINE> ALLIED PRODUCTS CORP. (Chicago)  </DATELINE><TEXT>    James J. Hayden,formerly president of the Automation division of RexnordInc., was named executive vice president and chief financialofficer of this maker of farm equipment and other goods. Aschief financial officer, he succeeds Richard Drexler, whocontinues as president and chief executive officer of thecompany.</TEXT></DOC>